title: A boat trip from Harderwijk to Urk (NL) in 1926 in color!

sources.title: A boat trip from Harderwijk to Urk (NL) in 1926 in color!
sources.description: Restored and colorized film about a boat trip across the Zuiderzee in The Netherlands from the fishing towns of Harderwijk to Urk almost a century ago in 1926.
